Haman ochano mondo otiek jo-Yahudi


1  Bang’ mano ruoth Ahasuerus nomiyo Haman wuod Hamedatha ja Agag duong’ moloyo, komiye bedo maduong’ moloyo jodongo duto mane en-go. 
2  Kuom mano jotich ruoth duto mane tiyo e dala ruoth ne kulore ni Haman, ka miye duong’ nikech ruoth nochiko mondo gitim kamano. To Mordekai ne ok kulrene, kendo ne ok miye duong’. 
3  Jotich mane tiyo e dala ne penjo Mordekai niya, “Marang’o iketho chik ruoth?” 
4  Ne giwuoyo kode kamano pile, to ne ok odew wechegi, omiyo ne ginyiso Haman mondo gine ane ka onyalo yie gi gima Mordekai timo, nikech Mordekai nosenyisogi ni en ja-Yahudi. 
5  Kane Haman oneno ni Mordeklai ok kulrene, kendo ok miye duong’, mirima nomake ahinya. 
6  To kane owinjo ni Mordekai en ja-Yahudi, noweyo paro mar nego Mordekai kende, to nochano tieko jo-Yahudi duto mane odak e pinje duto manie bwo loch ruoth Ahasuerus.


7  Kuom mano, e due mokwongo miluongo ni Nisan e higa mar apar gariyo mar loch ruoth Ahasuerus, ne gigoyo ombulu miluongo ni Pur e nyim Haman, mondo giyier odiechieng’ kod due mowinjore negie jo-Yahudi, mi ombulu noyiero chieng’ due apar gadek due mar apar gariyo, miluongo ni Adar. 
8  Eka Haman nowacho ni ruoth Ahasuerus niya, “Nitie oganda moro moke e kind ogendini manie pinje duto mae bwo lochni, ma chikegi opogore gi chike ogendini mamoko duto, to bende ok gidew kata mana chik ruoth. Omiyo ok owinjore iwegi aweya kamano. 
9  Kiyie to gol chik mondo otiek ogandano chuth. An abiro chulo fedha moromo kilo alufu mia adek, mondo jokeno magi oket kar kenoni.” 
10  Kuom mano ruoth nogolo tere e lwete, momiyo Haman wuod Hamedatha ja-Agag, ma jasik jo-Yahudi, 
11  kowachone niya, “Bed abeda gi pesani, kendo ji bende nie lweti. Timgi mana kaka ihero.”


12  Chieng’ due apar gadek due mokwongo, noluong jondiko mag ruoth, mi ondiko weche duto mane Haman ochiko. Ne gindiko ni jodongo kod jotend pinje duto kaachiel gi jodong ogendini te manie bwo loch ruoth, gi dhok ma piny ka piny, kendo oganda ka oganda nyalo somo kendo winjo. Ne ondikgi gi nying ruoth Ahasuerus, kendo noket kuomgi sei gi tere mar ruoth. 
13  Eka noor joote e pinje duto manie bwo loch ruoth gi barupe mondikie ni, jo-Yahudi nyaka negi mi tiek pep, bed ni gin joma dongo kata joma tindo, nyithindo kata mon. Mwandugi bende nyaka yaki. Chieng’ due apar gadek due mar apar gariyo, miluongo ni Adar ema noketi mondo oneggie.


14   Barupego nondikie niya:

An Ahasuerus ruoth maduong’, andiko baruani ni jotend pinje mia achiel gi piero ariyo gabiriyo manie bwo lochna, chakre Inia nyaka Ethiopia, kendo ni jotend pinje matindo manie bwogi.


15   “An gi loch kuom ogendini mang’eny, kendo an ruodh piny ngima, to ok aseyie mondo abed gi sunga nikech duong’ ma an-go, to asetiyo gi luor kod ng’wono mondo ami joga odag e ngima maonge tungni, ka adwaro mondo pinya obed gi kue ma ji duto dwaro, kendo obed kama ng’ato nyalo wuothoe kuonde duto maonge thagruok. 
16  Kane apenjo jong’adna rieko mondo onyisa gima wanyalo timo kuom wechego, achiel kuomgi ma nyinge Haman ne odwoka. En e ng’ama riek moloyo kuomwa, kendo en ng’ama ogen ahinya nikech osetiyonwa aming’a maonge ketho, kochiwore chutho, bende en jalupna. 
17  Ne onyisowa ni nitie oganda moro moke e kind ogendini duto, ma chikegi miyo ok ginyal winjore gi ogendini mamoko duto. Gin ema pile gichayo chike ma ruoth golo, omiyo chik mane wagolo mondo wariw piny obed achiel ok nyal tiyo.


18   “Kamano, waseng’eyo ni jogo kende ema ok winjre gi ji mamoko duto, nikech chikegi magalagalago opogogi kodgi. Bende ok giyie gi lochwa, to gitimo richo madongo ahinya manyalo ketho kue mar piny.


19   “Kuom mano, wamiyou chik mondo uneg jogo duto ma nyinggi ondik e barupe ma Haman, mane waketo jarit piny, kendo ma en kaka wuonwa mar ariyo, oseoronu. Ber mondo otiekgi chutho, kaachiel gi mondgi kod nyithindgi, chieng’ due apar gang’wen due mar apar gariyo mar higani, ma en due mar Adar, kinegogi gi ligangla mag wasikgi mak ong’wonnigi kata matin. 
20  Kamano mondo joma pile osebedo kapiem, oneg odiechieng’ achiel mondo lochwa ogurre motegno, kendo piny obed gi kue mosiko.”


21  Nondik weche mag chikno, moor ni pinje duto mae bwo loch ruoth, mondo oland ni ogendini duto, oikre ni chieng’no.


22  Jootego nowuok piyopiyo, kaka ruoth nochiko, bende ne ogo milomb wachno e dala maduong’ mar Susa. Haman gi ruoth ne jobet kametho. Jo-Susa to nobwok kowinjo wachno.

